{"id":138769,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/03/简讯：沙特宣布禁止一切示威游行/","date":"2011-03-06T17:20:35Z","modified":"2011-03-06T17:20:35Z","title":"简讯：沙特宣布禁止一切示威游行","content":"<div>\n<p>沙特阿拉伯国家电视台宣布政府声明，禁止一切示威游行活动。</p>\n<p>内政部的声明说，沙特安全部队将采取一切措施，阻止任何企图破坏公共秩序的行为。</p>\n<p>记者们说，在国家电视台宣布这项声明之前，沙特东部的一个产油省份曾发生由什叶派少数群体举行的小规模抗议示威。</p>\n</p></div>\n<div>\n</div>\n<p><a href=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/-yDDteRv3YEGfhgiJEhZJs0mE3g/0/da\"><img border=\"0\" ismap src=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/-yDDteRv3YEGfhgiJEhZJs0mE3g/0/di\"></a><br />\n<a href=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/-yDDteRv3YEGfhgiJEhZJs0mE3g/1/da\"><img border=\"0\" ismap src=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/-yDDteRv3YEGfhgiJEhZJs0mE3g/1/di\"></a></p>\n<div>\n<a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?a=t4fBWu5leVA:RpJiithNs_I:mqyYa2mfVbY\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?d=mqyYa2mfVbY\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?a=t4fBWu5leVA:RpJiithNs_I:PFx2F_oWK34\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?d=PFx2F_oWK34\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?a=t4fBWu5leVA:RpJiithNs_I:DUWcskeyX7o\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?d=DUWcskeyX7o\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?a=t4fBWu5leVA:RpJiithNs_I:clraHZBW0_I\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?d=clraHZBW0_I\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?a=t4fBWu5leVA:RpJiithNs_I:qj6IDK7rITs\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?d=qj6IDK7rITs\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?a=t4fBWu5leVA:RpJiithNs_I:7Q72WNTAKBA\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?d=7Q72WNTAKBA\" /></a>\n</div>\n<p><img height=\"1\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/cnbbc/~4/t4fBWu5leVA\" width=\"1\" /></p>\n<p><b>要翻墙？(发邮件到Gmail):ziyouwangluo2011ATgmail.com</b></p>\n","author":176,"categories":[87